OL,6,FSo, while she studies to become a
OL,7,Fmidwife in the hope of a brighter
OL,8,Ffuture, Saskia and Edie are living in
OL,9,Fa housing association property and are
OL,10,Fleft with just #20 a month to live on.
OL,12,FWhile she keeps her financial
OL,13,Fstruggles a secret from her daughter,
OL,14,FSaskia says she fears Edie will think
OL,15,F"Father Christmas loves her less" than
OL,16,Fother children.
