OL,3,CMum left skipping meals as she
OL,4,Cstruggles to clothe toddler this winter
OL,6,F"I don't want Edie to know that we
OL,7,Fdon't have any money," Saskia said. "I
OL,8,Fkeep it all away from her and when I'm
OL,9,Freally struggling I just make sure
OL,10,Fthere's food on the table for her and
OL,11,Fthere's money to put the heating on."
OL,13,FSaskia says winter brings particular
OL,14,Fchallenges, as Edie needs new clothes
OL,15,Fand a warm house.
OL,17,F"I'm worried about keeping her warm
OL,18,Fbecause it's really hard to buy her
OL,19,Floads of warm clothes," she said.
