OL,3,CMum left skipping meals as she
OL,4,Cstruggles to clothe toddler this winter
OL,6,F"Because she's a toddler, she goes
OL,7,Fthrough clothes really quickly. It's
OL,8,Fworrying. I don't want her to be cold.
OL,9,FBut I can't afford to keep the heating
OL,10,Fon."
OL,12,FPrioritising the needs of her daughter
OL,13,Fmeans Saskia regularly goes without
OL,14,Fherself.
