OL,3,CMum left skipping meals as she
OL,4,Cstruggles to clothe toddler this winter
OL,6,F"When she starts school, I don't want
OL,7,Fher to think Father Christmas loves
OL,8,Fher less because she didn't get as
OL,9,Fmuch as some other children."
OL,11,FEven Saskia's plans to go to
OL,12,Funiversity come with their own set of
OL,13,Fworries.
OL,15,F"I'm doing an access to midwifery
OL,16,Fcourse which is expensive, but I've
OL,17,Fbudgeted and taken expenditure from
OL,18,Fother places to try to better my
OL,19,Fsituation and get to university," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
