OL,3,CMum left skipping meals as she
OL,4,Cstruggles to clothe toddler this winter
OL,6,F"But then just getting to university
OL,7,Fis another worry because of the
OL,8,Fdistance it is from my home and the
OL,9,Flack of financial help for students
OL,10,Fthat are also parents."
OL,12,FAt the moment, the amount of Universal
OL,13,FCredit people are entitled to changes
OL,14,Fdepending on their age - with over-25s
OL,15,Fgetting more.
OL,17,FSaskia is calling for this to change.
