OL,3,CMum left skipping meals as she
OL,4,Cstruggles to clothe toddler this winter
OL,6,F"I think if you're a parent and under
OL,7,F25, you should get the same amount of
OL,8,Fstandard living allowance as someone
OL,9,Felse does," she said.
OL,11,F"Just because I'm a parent under 25
OL,12,Fdoesn't mean I have any less bills. I
OL,13,Fhave the same amount of bills, I have
OL,14,Fthe same amount of rent, I still have
OL,15,Fto pay the same amount but I get about
OL,16,F#80 less a month - that #80 would do
OL,17,Fso much for my family. I could afford
OL,18,Fto put the heading on, I could buy
OL,19,Ftoys and clothes."
